Simple method to disable CotH for a given area is to define a section (like a 3D volume of space) and say &quot;within this, CotH is non-castable). They manage to do this all over the place, Elem Planes, Tactics, etc.. Nightmare, a new zone for the hedge maze isn't needed (and wouldn't work for the quest anyways, as zoning wipes local state data from an npc, such as hate list, whatnot), only that the area be marked unCotHable. Easy.<br>
